OL,4,Cdementia calls for ban on heading ball
OL,6,FThe widow of an ex-Manchester United
OL,7,Fplayer who died from dementia is
OL,8,Fcalling for a ban on heading footballs
OL,9,Fon what should have been his 75th
OL,10,Fbirthday.
OL,12,FFrank Kopel died in 2014 aged 65,
OL,13,Fafter a career which included playing
OL,14,Ffor Dundee United, Blackburn Rovers,
OL,15,Fand Arbroath and Forfar Athletic.
