OL,3,CWidow of footballer who died from
OL,4,Cdementia calls for ban on heading ball
OL,6,FMike said: "We learn from an early age
OL,7,Fnot to handle the ball, surely we can
OL,8,Flearn not to head it either.
OL,10,F"Scotland has led the way by banning
OL,11,Fchildren from heading the ball in
OL,12,Ftraining and adult players from
OL,13,Fheading in the 24 hours before and
OL,14,Fafter a game.
OL,16,F"I'd like to see the practice banned
OL,17,Faltogether after the 2030 World Cup,
OL,18,Fwhich I think is a reasonable deadline.
OL,20,F"Not heading the ball will save
OL,21,Fplayers' lives."
