OL,6,FIn 2021, The FA introduced Heading
OL,7,FGuidance in Training which eliminated
OL,8,For restricted heading at age under 12
OL,9,Fand below.
OL,11,FThe association said it wanted to
OL,12,Falign matchday with training in these
OL,13,Fage groups and continue the trial the
OL,14,Fremoval of deliberate heading in
OL,15,Fcompetitions and matches.
